OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FBy US Correspondent Dan Rivers, with
OL,7,Fadditional reporting by Washington
OL,8,FNews Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,10,FIn Cuba, power is everything.
OL,12,FNot just the influence the Communist
OL,13,Fgovernment wields over the people, but
OL,14,Falso the electricity, vital for so
OL,15,Fmuch of modern life.
OL,17,FCubans' ability to watch TV, read, and
OL,18,Flive with dignity is being suffocated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
