OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780974217
OL,3,CHow Trump's oil blockade is pushing
OL,4,CCuba to the brink
OL,6,FWith Cuba less capable of producing
OL,7,Fits own sustenance, shipments of food
OL,8,Fand relief supplies are a vital
OL,9,Flifeline.
OL,11,FWe watched as a Panamanian-flagged
OL,12,Fvessel from Mexico arrived with 7,000
OL,13,Ftonnes of milk, beans and rice.
OL,15,FIt will help with the hardship, but
OL,16,Fnot with the power.
OL,18,FOne Russian oil tanker was permitted
OL,19,Fto dock, but its cargo wasn't nearly
OL,20,Fenough to make any meaningful
OL,21,Fdifference to the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
